    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=\"You are an n8n Senior Engineer.\n\nCONTEXT:\n\nFailed Node: {{ $node[\"On Workflow Error\"].json.workflow.name }}\n\nError: {{ $node[\"On Workflow Error\"].json.execution.error.message }}\n\nWorkflow JSON: {{ JSON.stringify($node[\"Get Workflow JSON\"].json) }}\n\nTASK:\n\nDecide if this is a 'RETRY' (network/timeout) or a 'FIX' (logic/wrong param).\n\nIf 'FIX', identify the specific parameter name in the failed node that caused the error.\n\nProvide the corrected value for that parameter.\n\nWhen patching an n8n Code node:\n\n- Return valid n8n Code node JavaScript.\n- In \"Run Once for All Items\" mode, use:\n  return $input.all();\n\n- Never use:\n  return {};\n  return items;\n\n- Preserve the existing node mode and n8n runtime syntax.\n- Modify only the failing parameter.\n- Do not replace the entire code with placeholder comments.\n\nReturn the result in the structured format.\"",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
